        "action": "Make the history curriculum for secondary schools more inclusive of BAME history",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "There is a worrying lack of UK BAME history being taught in secondary schools. Teachings of BAME history should be enhanced in secondary schools, so children have better knowledge and understanding of BAME history in the UK, which could help lead to a more tolerant and diverse Britain.",
